<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 16:09:19 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队公布了在加沙地带遇难的另外三名士兵的姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-releases-names-of-three-additional-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-strip/0000018b-d8a5-d168-a3ef-ddff591c0000</link><description>以色列军队迄今公布了自10月7日与哈马斯开战以来阵亡的371名士兵的名字</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 16:04:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-releases-names-of-three-additional-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-strip/0000018b-d8a5-d168-a3ef-ddff591c0000</guid></item><item><title>长期被忽视且资金不足的以色列精神卫生系统无法治疗所有 10 月 7 日幸存者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/long-neglected-and-underfunded-israels-mental-health-system-unable-to-handle-survivors/0000018b-d4db-d168-a3ef-d5fb34660000</link><description>卫生部长表示，自战争爆发以来，约有10万人遭受过创伤性事件，而该系统还没有做好应对的准备。 “战争是全国性的心理健康事件”</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 15:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/long-neglected-and-underfunded-israels-mental-health-system-unable-to-handle-survivors/0000018b-d4db-d168-a3ef-d5fb34660000</guid></item><item><title>核掩体中的艺术：10 月 7 日，以色列博物馆进入战时模式</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-october-7-israels-museums-implemented-emergency-wartime-plans-to-save-their-art/0000018b-d867-df9a-ab8b-deeff65c0000</link><description>哈马斯渗透以色列后几个小时内，该国最大的博物馆紧急保护其最重要的物品，并将艺术品转入地下</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 15:10:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-october-7-israels-museums-implemented-emergency-wartime-plans-to-save-their-art/0000018b-d867-df9a-ab8b-deeff65c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙的战争不会削弱哈马斯的政治影响力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-in-gaza-wont-diminish-hamas-political-influence/0000018b-d4db-df9a-ab8b-dedb12940000</link><description>哈马斯不仅仅是一个单纯通过军事行动就能消灭的恐怖组织。他们的金融和政治触角伸向世界各地，对以色列摧毁他们的承诺构成了重大障碍</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 15:01:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-in-gaza-wont-diminish-hamas-political-influence/0000018b-d4db-df9a-ab8b-dedb12940000</guid></item><item><title>这位大屠杀幸存者希望招募纽约犹太人重建他的基布兹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/this-massacre-survivor-is-hoping-to-enlist-n-y-jews-in-rebuilding-his-kibbutz/0000018b-d80d-df9a-ab8b-decda9b00000</link><description>Or Yelin 正在纽约进行为期八天的筹款之旅，他希望为 10 月 7 日哈马斯暴行后遭受创伤的贝埃里基布兹 (Kibbutz Be&amp;#39;eri) 成员筹集 1200 万美元</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 14:47:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/this-massacre-survivor-is-hoping-to-enlist-n-y-jews-in-rebuilding-his-kibbutz/0000018b-d80d-df9a-ab8b-decda9b00000</guid></item><item><title>与哈马斯的战争期间，以色列阿拉伯社区的凶杀率下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/homicide-rate-in-israels-arab-community-drops-during-war-with-hamas/0000018b-d4db-df9a-ab8b-dedb38c50000</link><description>与 9 月份相比，谋杀案数量下降了 60%。专家将数量减少归因于更严格的执法，但警告称战争结束后数量将再次激增</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 14:33:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/homicide-rate-in-israels-arab-community-drops-during-war-with-hamas/0000018b-d4db-df9a-ab8b-dedb38c50000</guid></item><item><title>南非政府是哈马斯和伊朗毫无歉意、无耻的代理人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/south-africas-government-is-an-unapologetic-shameless-proxy-for-hamas-and-iran/0000018b-d7d9-dffa-adef-f7d979970000</link><description>政府部长和哈马斯领导人之间的色情、阿谀奉承的恋情，对伊朗的热烈拥抱，明确呼吁攻击犹太人、我们的家园、我们的工作场所、我们的学校。我们南非犹太人想知道我们自己的政府是否正在煽动针对我们的大屠杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 13:51:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/south-africas-government-is-an-unapologetic-shameless-proxy-for-hamas-and-iran/0000018b-d7d9-dffa-adef-f7d979970000</guid></item><item><title>埃里温犹太教堂在亚美尼亚武装组织反犹太主义袭击中纵火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/yerevan-synagogue-set-on-fire-in-antisemitic-attack-by-armenian-militant-group/0000018b-d7ed-d423-affb-f7efb5d90000</link><description>据称，这次袭击是为了声援巴勒斯坦和黎巴嫩反对犹太复国主义的抵抗运动。该武装组织表示指责以色列支持阿塞拜疆，阿塞拜疆被指控对纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫的亚美尼亚人犯下战争罪</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 13:39:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/yerevan-synagogue-set-on-fire-in-antisemitic-attack-by-armenian-militant-group/0000018b-d7ed-d423-affb-f7efb5d90000</guid></item><item><title>拜登高级官员对约旦河西岸可能爆发另一条战线表示担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/u-s-officials-express-concern-about-possible-eruption-of-another-front-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-d79f-d423-affb-f7bf32040000</link><description>随着以色列继续对加沙进行地面入侵，美国官员担心约旦河西岸的相对平静可能很快演变成一场全面战争 — — 这是美国和以色列在政治上都无法承受的</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 13:05:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/u-s-officials-express-concern-about-possible-eruption-of-another-front-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-d79f-d423-affb-f7bf32040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯战争结束后，本·拉登为 9/11 所做的辩护在 TikTok 上疯传</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/bin-ladens-justification-for-9-11-goes-viral-on-tiktok-in-wake-of-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-d80f-df9a-ab8b-decf2c9c0000</link><description>这封信周三疯传后，《卫报》将其从网站上删除</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 12:57:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/bin-ladens-justification-for-9-11-goes-viral-on-tiktok-in-wake-of-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-d80f-df9a-ab8b-decf2c9c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突的两国解决方案目前不可行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/a-two-state-solution-to-the-israel-palestine-conflict-is-currently-unviable/0000018b-d76b-dffa-adef-f76b885b0000</link><description>10月7日事件发生后，两国模式被视为幻想，同时也成为许多争论的话题。但在不久的将来的某个时刻，人们将会认识到当前的情况是不可持续的。那时这个想法将真正卷土重来。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 12:51:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/a-two-state-solution-to-the-israel-palestine-conflict-is-currently-unviable/0000018b-d76b-dffa-adef-f76b885b0000</guid></item><item><title>雷吉娜·斯佩克托：“许多像我一样的犹太人仍然处于震惊和悲伤之中”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/regina-spektor-many-jews-like-me-are-still-in-shock-and-sorrow/0000018b-d790-dffa-adef-f790f2900000</link><description>这位犹太裔美国歌手对 10 月 7 日之后反犹太主义的兴起感到惊讶，并发现自己从那时起就在社交媒体上争论不休。她对她的英雄尤其失望，其中包括冰岛音乐家比约克，他们对哈马斯的残酷袭击做出了反应。 “感觉就像喝下水道的水，”她告诉《国土报》</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 12:25:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/regina-spektor-many-jews-like-me-are-still-in-shock-and-sorrow/0000018b-d790-dffa-adef-f790f2900000</guid></item><item><title>自加沙战争爆发以来，进步民主党首次发起阻止美国向以色列出售武器的行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/progressive-democrats-launch-first-effort-to-block-arms-sales-to-israel-since-gaza-war/0000018b-d7be-d423-affb-f7bf71070000</link><description>众议员伊尔汗·奥马尔领导的反对决议呼吁阻止向以色列转让价值 3.2 亿美元的精确制导炸弹设备，因为以色列与哈马斯的战争已接近第七周</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 12:07:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/progressive-democrats-launch-first-effort-to-block-arms-sales-to-israel-since-gaza-war/0000018b-d7be-d423-affb-f7bf71070000</guid></item><item><title>新民意调查显示，美国犹太选民绝大多数支持拜登处理以色列-加沙战争的方式</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/u-s-jewish-voters-overwhelmingly-back-bidens-handling-of-israel-gaza-war-new-poll-shows/0000018b-d7ef-dffa-adef-f7effc400000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以来首次对美国犹太选民进行的民意调查显示，74% 的人支持拜登在以色列和加沙问题上的做法 ■ 犹太选民对拜登在打击反犹太主义方面的信任程度远远超过特朗普 ■ 68% 的人支持拜登而非特朗普</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 12:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/u-s-jewish-voters-overwhelmingly-back-bidens-handling-of-israel-gaza-war-new-poll-shows/0000018b-d7ef-dffa-adef-f7effc400000</guid></item><item><title>难以忽视的事实是以色列将不得不重建加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/the-inconvenient-truth-is-that-israel-will-have-to-rebuild-gaza/0000018b-d7e4-dffa-adef-f7e4f0ec0000</link><description>必须有人对飞地负责，而以色列是唯一现实的候选人。这是一项不受欢迎但必要的任务</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 11:40:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/the-inconvenient-truth-is-that-israel-will-have-to-rebuild-gaza/0000018b-d7e4-dffa-adef-f7e4f0ec0000</guid></item><item><title>在战争时期，以色列的极端正统派为世俗犹太人提供了一座桥梁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-time-of-war-israels-ultra-orthodox-offer-a-bridge-to-secular-jews/0000018b-d794-d423-affb-f7b714900000</link><description>哈马斯史无前例的屠杀引发了一些人的反思，并改变了正统社会对服兵役的看法。目前，许多人正在志愿帮助撤离人员和士兵做出贡献</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 11:06:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-time-of-war-israels-ultra-orthodox-offer-a-bridge-to-secular-jews/0000018b-d794-d423-affb-f7b714900000</guid></item><item><title>新理论声称，耶路撒冷失落的圣经纪念碑清晰可见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-16/ty-article/lost-biblical-monument-in-jerusalem-is-in-plain-sight-new-theory-claims/0000018b-d20c-dffa-adef-f60ce9be0000</link><description>研究表明，耶路撒冷基训泉周围的巨大防御工事可能是圣经中所罗门建造的神秘的“米洛”</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 10:56:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-16/ty-article/lost-biblical-monument-in-jerusalem-is-in-plain-sight-new-theory-claims/0000018b-d20c-dffa-adef-f60ce9be0000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼 MK 被任命代表政府参加有争议的司法小组</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/far-right-mk-tapped-to-represent-government-in-disputed-judicial-panel/0000018b-d787-df9a-ab8b-dfcf75d40000</link><description>宗教犹太复国主义议员奥里特·斯特罗克 (Orit Strock) 在周四的委员会会议之前当选，这是自 2022 年底政府成立以来的第一次会议。司法部长亚里夫·莱文 (Yariv Levin) 在向高等法院提出请愿后决定召开该委员会会议，寻求迫使他这样做所以</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 10:19:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/far-right-mk-tapped-to-represent-government-in-disputed-judicial-panel/0000018b-d787-df9a-ab8b-dfcf75d40000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯大屠杀后，十月份寻求枪支许可证的以色列人急剧增加</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/dramatic-increase-in-israelis-seeking-gun-permits-in-october-following-hamas-massacre/0000018b-d4db-d423-affb-f7fb34610000</link><description>国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔强调公民防卫工作的必要性，敦促任何有资格的人“即使在今天也要这样做”；其他人则警告大规模分发枪支的后果</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 10:11:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/dramatic-increase-in-israelis-seeking-gun-permits-in-october-following-hamas-massacre/0000018b-d4db-d423-affb-f7fb34610000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯大屠杀后失踪的 12 岁以色列女孩的家人放弃希望，告别</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/giving-up-hope-family-of-girl-12-missing-since-massacre-say-goodbye/0000018b-d4db-df9a-ab8b-dedb37350000</link><description>来自贝埃里基布兹 (Kibbutz Be&amp;#39;eri) 的 12 岁女孩 Liel Hetzroni 的家人决定将她的物品埋在尸体的地方。 “莉尔被谋杀的事实很清楚，”一位亲戚在向莉尔告别时说道，莉尔被认为已经死亡，旁边还有她的双胞胎兄弟、阿姨和祖父，他们都于 10 月 7 日被杀。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 10:04:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/giving-up-hope-family-of-girl-12-missing-since-massacre-say-goodbye/0000018b-d4db-df9a-ab8b-dedb37350000</guid></item></channel></rss>